---
import beforeAfterMen1 from '@/assets/images/b6de27df4c69.webp';
import beforeAfterMen2 from '@/assets/images/bcdc3a29fdee.webp';
---

<section class="section prp-h-s4">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prp-h-s4__layout">

      <div class="prp-h-s4__text-col">

        <h2 class="prp-h-s4__heading">The Platelet-Rich Plasma Hair Restoration Solution</h2>

        <p class="prp-h-s4__body">PRP Hair Restoration is a cutting-edge, non-surgical treatment that uses the regenerative power of your own blood to stimulate natural hair growth and combat thinning.</p>

        <ul class="prp-h-s4__feature-list">
          <li>Derived from your own blood, no foreign substances</li>
          <li>Targets the root cause of hair loss at the follicle level</li>
          <li>Stimulates dormant follicles to re-enter the growth phase</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="prp-h-s4__body">The process begins with a simple blood draw. Your blood is then placed in a centrifuge, which spins it at high speed to separate and concentrate the platelets. This platelet-rich plasma is packed with growth factors that, when injected into the scalp, trigger natural hair regrowth.</p>

        <p class="prp-h-s4__body">At Menon Medispa, this treatment is performed under the direction of Dr. Aditi Menon, a regenerative medicine specialist who ensures precision and care in every session.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="prp-h-s4__img-col">
        <div class="prp-h-s4__img-pair">
          <div class="prp-h-s4__img-wrap">
            <img
              src={beforeAfterMen1.src}
              alt="Before and After Men Hair Restoration at Menon Medispa"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              width="336"
              height="334"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="prp-h-s4__img-wrap">
            <img
              src={beforeAfterMen2.src}
              alt="Before and After Men Hair Restoration at Menon Medispa"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              width="330"
              height="334"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .prp-h-s4__layout {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__text-col {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .prp-h-s4__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .prp-h-s4__feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__feature-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.5em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .prp-h-s4__feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-cta);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__img-col {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 340px;
  }

  .prp-h-s4__img-pair {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__img-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .prp-h-s4__img-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .prp-h-s4__img-col {
      width: 280px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prp-h-s4__layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .prp-h-s4__img-col {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 340px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
